            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_105gc' title='Col. 105GC &mdash; HL Deb 17 March 2004 vol 659 c105GC' name='column_105gc' href='#column_105gc' rel='bookmark'>105GC</a>
            should be held in some way responsible for the standards of care adopted by other members of the team? In effect, that is what this clause attempts to do.
