      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0659P0-01876'>
        <a name='S5LV0659P0_20040317_GCR_159'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-sainsbury' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0659P0_20040317_GCR_159' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Sainsbury' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
