          <p class='first-para'>
            I agree absolutely with the point made by my noble friend Lord Wedderburn. In an earlier amendment we made the distinction between
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_125gc' title='Col. 125GC &mdash; HL Deb 17 March 2004 vol 659 c125GC' name='column_125gc' href='#column_125gc' rel='bookmark'>125GC</a>
            what a finance director should know and what a sales director should know. So I agree with my noble friend on this.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0659P0-01908'>
        <a name='S5LV0659P0_20040317_GCR_191'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-macgregor' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0659P0_20040317_GCR_191' title='Link to this speech by Mr John MacGregor' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
