          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0659P0_20040317_GCR_252' title='Link to this speech by Mr Matthew Evans' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-matthew-evans" title="Mr Matthew Evans">Lord Evans of Temple Guiting</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
